## Clinical Neutrality Clause

> **Scope Restriction on Representation and Redistribution**  
>  
> This software may not be publicly represented, promoted, or redistributed as part of an **anti-corporate**, **anti-Microsoft**, or **ideologically adversarial** campaign.  
>  
> While the software includes telemetry-reducing configurations and developer autonomy features, its purpose is purely technical:  
> to give users precise control over their .NET development environments.

Any redistribution must:

- Accurately reflect this purpose  
- Avoid inflammatory framing or commercial positioning that distorts the intent of the project  

Violations may result in revocation of redistribution rights under Section 6 of the GPLv3.

